{"tid":1776043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女權組織要人- 正尋找「警察性暴力」證人/受害者, 提供資料, 協助國際游說","createTime":"2019-12-09T08:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T07:08:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0371bd20ad1dd08a35aac8459ad8ef8a056ee01a","tid":1776043,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:58:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=7a483108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"55609e5fd48b09df955e1dab2584dadc7c587e67","tid":1776043,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be63da490b827ae89a444a7c1db32517fa8a0af2","tid":1776043,"uid":40520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"叫d醫護狗做野啦"},{"pid":"1c184d30d55bc83823052f049444ed1d9a91ccb7","tid":1776043,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be63da490b827ae89a444a7c1db32517fa8a0af2","tid":1776043,"uid":40520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"叫d醫護狗做野啦"},"citedBy":0,"r